        <guid>https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/Fold%20Craft%20Launcher.png" alt="Featured image of post Fold Craft Launcher 教程" /&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;下载-fold-craft-launcher&#34;&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%e4%b8%8b%e8%bd%bd-fold-craft-launcher&#34; class=&#34;header-anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    下载 Fold Craft Launcher
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;前往 &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/FCL-Team/FoldCraftLauncher&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Github 项目地址&lt;/a&gt;下载最新发行版的 Fold Craft Launcher&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/github-repo.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2560&#34;
	height=&#34;1403&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/github-repo_huae1650cc981799cff7a47b356766876b_448887_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/github-repo_huae1650cc981799cff7a47b356766876b_448887_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;github-repo&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;182&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;437px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;下载适合自己设备的版本&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/releases.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2560&#34;
	height=&#34;1249&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/releases_hu9d49f2cf0c7f6e1aa5d4b0a7c8ac0d92_270615_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/releases_hu9d49f2cf0c7f6e1aa5d4b0a7c8ac0d92_270615_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;releases&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;204&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;491px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;配置-fold-craft-launcher&#34;&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%e9%85%8d%e7%bd%ae-fold-craft-launcher&#34; class=&#34;header-anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    配置 Fold Craft Launcher
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;下载安装完成后直接点击安装所需环境&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image01.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2560&#34;
	height=&#34;1152&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image01_huc54cf1110ff8d6a2dc89bbe81eb2ad35_2245762_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image01_huc54cf1110ff8d6a2dc89bbe81eb2ad35_2245762_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;222&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;533px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;点击添加账户，完成第三方认证&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image02.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2560&#34;
	height=&#34;1152&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image02_hu8d47e2ee13f72c4d9839e52d84d49b5e_1282705_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image02_hu8d47e2ee13f72c4d9839e52d84d49b5e_1282705_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;222&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;533px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image03.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2560&#34;
	height=&#34;1152&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image03_huc960e93286fcae40f9e3a150dd08d21f_1233293_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image03_huc960e93286fcae40f9e3a150dd08d21f_1233293_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;222&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;533px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image04.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2560&#34;
	height=&#34;1152&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image04_hu504cebc63502c9aa0ab050e52064fba0_601506_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image04_hu504cebc63502c9aa0ab050e52064fba0_601506_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;222&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;533px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;例如&lt;code&gt;Littleskin&lt;/code&gt;的认证服务器：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-text&#34; data-lang=&#34;text&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;https://littleskin.cn/api/yggdrasil
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;登录所属认证服务器的账号&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image05.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2560&#34;
	height=&#34;1152&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image05_hud0e8ea50a702190d28abc02e71b0f355_608387_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image05_hud0e8ea50a702190d28abc02e71b0f355_608387_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;222&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;533px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;登录完成后，下载想要版本的游戏&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://5i-tomato.github.io/p/fold-craft-launcher-tutorial/image06.png&#34;
